Homepage: I prototyped the home page in its entirety.
LINK: https://github.com/zuri-training/Favicon-Gen-team62/issues/63


About us: I designed the about us page. A page that tells guests and registered users more details about the platform. I also added the micro-interactions to make it intuitive.
LINK: https://github.com/zuri-training/Favicon-Gen-team62/issues/64


Login / Register / Forgot Password: I didn't design these pages. What I did was to prototype and link all the corresponding pages to make the user journey seamless.
LINK: https://github.com/zuri-training/Favicon-Gen-team62/issues/49


Generate From Image: This page was about how users that want to generate favicons from their choice of images. Images that users already had are uploaded on this page and the platform generates the favicon automatically. I designed and prototyped this page.
LINK: https://github.com/zuri-training/Favicon-Gen-team62/issues/46


Navigation Bar: I designed the platform navigation bar taking into account users that are logged in and those that are guest users.
LINK: https://github.com/zuri-training/Favicon-Gen-team62/issues/45


